com.squareup.picasso

Interface Target


  • public interface Target
    Represents an arbitrary listener for image loading.

    Objects implementing this class must have a working implementation of #equals(Object) and #hashCode() for proper storage internally. Instances of this interface will also be compared to determine if view recycling is occurring. It is recommended that you add this interface directly on to a custom view type when using in an adapter to ensure correct recycling behavior.
